Regarding the images for your new website, you can make them yourself by way of just composing said images through the paint program on your computer or even through the use of a scanner for your photos as well as other hardcopy images. If you need to come with an image from another website for your website, remember to first ask who owns the web site to get permission. Due to copyright laws, you have to gain this permission in the owner to legitimately use said images for your own personel purposes.

To publish your new website, have any File Transfer Protocol program. Open said FTP program and sign in by inputting the username and password. Go to the directory where your own homepage is situated. When you are there, just start the process of uploading each and every webpage and graphic of your new website based on the exact instructions of FTP program and, obviously, even the actual host server you are using. There, you have done it! Following this last step, you have succeeded in the process of how to build an internet site.